A bus travel agency provides the travel and tourism services for the buses. The bus
travel agency provides the tourism related services like show the booklet of plans for the trip
booking of plans, payment cancellation accept the data of the customer.
When the customer ask for particular location then agency shows the booklet of that
particular location .After getting infomenu.cssrmation about all plans if customer is satisfied with that
plans or with that dates then he/she will book any one of the plan and if customer is not
satisfied with that plan then he/she will ask for any other plan.
After selecting the plan the customer will book that plan for the booking process the
customer have to give details like name, contact no, age no of passengers. After giving the
details the admin checks the availability of the no of seats. If number of seats are not available
then customer may have to select any other trip and if no of seats are available then the
admin will book that particular trip for that customer. After booking of that trip the next
process is payment for the payment options are card payment and cash payment .If customer
select card payment then customer will have to give the pin of that card and cu stomer select
cash payment then customer have to give cash .After the payment of particular amount the
admin will give the receipt of the payment and give the ticket of that plan.
In case the customer has to cancel the whole rules of the trip then he has to go to the
agency and ask if return to the admin. Then admin will check rules and regulation and to
compute the refund customer can cancel some people going on a trip after he books a trip the
amount to be refunded depends on the no of people who have cancelled from the trip of the
individual in this case customer will get the new ticket with the details of the remaining
travelers
